{"tid":2287766,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日揆關注國安法 促港維持自由","createTime":"2020-11-16T04:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T04:26:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43decbc33b253a12eff288fd36610998bcfe9b8c","tid":2287766,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/37JGNPLWINA4TI3ZX6QOLMAOPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2F37JGNPLWINA4TI3ZX6QOLMAOPU%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3guBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=c8cf2295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2F37JGNPLWINA4TI3ZX6QOLMAOPU%2F&h=a5b8b94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/37JGNPLWINA4TI3ZX6QOLMAOPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n日揆關注國安法 促港維持自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yWfS_R5PRSVTYd1crlEorlgc9fE=/1386x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KBFULPGH4FAUBHCLDZTHI2XL2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyWfS_R5PRSVTYd1crlEorlgc9fE%3D%2F1386x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKBFULPGH4FAUBHCLDZTHI2XL2Y.jpg&h=c423950d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日本首相菅義偉前天在東亞峯會發表視像講話，對北京藉國安法加強控制香港表示重大憂慮。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【東亞峯會】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。。。。他又在東海及南海問題上批評中國，指摘中國在兩個海域進行加劇緊張的行動。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉前天透過視像出席有東盟十國、中、韓、俄等18國參加的東亞峯會，發言時多番批評中國。他表示，日本顧慮中國在尖閣諸島（中方稱為釣魚島）周邊的活動，批評中國「繼續在東海進行侵害日本主權的活動」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥中國令南海局勢升溫<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉又指中國在南海進行軍事化和彈道導彈演習，對中方違反法治和不符聯合國海洋法公約主張的應對做法表示擔憂。日本《產經新聞》稱，大部份與會國都在會議上對南海局勢表示擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n中國總理李克強在峯會發表視像講話時，未有回應日方就香港問題提出的批評，但重申中方將與東盟國家一同全面有效落實《南海各方行為宣言》，穩步推進「南海行為準則」，希望各方尊重地區國家維護南海和平穩定的努力。"}]}